      "content": "it's kinda weird though because i dont think i have much wax, and it happened right after the pop. i'm a bit worried it's more serious than just wax. u think i should really wait a few days to see if it clears up before i bother calling a doctor? i really dont want to go to the clinic if it's just an ear thing.",
