      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i'm feeling a little lightheaded too, and the hearing loss is pretty total on that side. i'm pretty sure i'm just stressed about it. any chance it's just my blood pressure or something and i can just sleep it off? i'd rather just take some ibuprofen and wait until the morning if that's fine.",
